  <summary date="2025-08-06T19:35:21Z" status="Introduced in Senate">North Platte Canteen Congressional Gold Medal Act

This bill provides for the award of a Congressional Gold Medal to recognize the individuals and communities that provided financial and other support for the North Platte Canteen in North Platte, Nebraska, during World War II.</summary>
